Bart.message: Hey! Ready to start the game?
Put the green cup on the red square mat at the far left centre of the table
Put the orange cup on the red circle mat at the left top of the table
Put the red whole apple on the orange square mat at the left centre of the table
Put the red sliced apple on the orange square mat at the left middle centre of the table
Put the brown bowl on the indigo square mat at the right middle centre of the table
Put the brown bread on the iris square mat at the right bottom of the table
Congratulations. We are done with the game. Thanks for playing
